  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/nikos/ontologies/2026/6/untitled-ontology-29#bornInRegion">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty"/>
    <rdfs:label>born in region (transitive closure)</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment>Derived relation: a Character bornInRegion any Location reachable by following bornIn and then zero-or-more locatedIn hops. Defined via an owl:propertyChainAxiom (bornIn o locatedIn -&gt; bornInRegion) plus bornIn being declared a sub-property of bornInRegion, so the reasoner computes this without any of it being asserted by hand.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/nikos/ontologies/2026/6/untitled-ontology-29#Character"/>
    <rdfs:range rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/nikos/ontologies/2026/6/untitled-ontology-29#Location"/>
    <owl:propertyChainAxiom rdf:nodeID="n4fe50af84ed34c0ba80820471fa44140b1"/>
  </rdf:Description>
