    <rdfs:label>has captain</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment>Relates an Organization to the Character who captains it. Inverse of isCaptainOf. NOTE: domain/range for the inverse-facing direction are declared on isCaptainOf below; this property is kept for backward navigation from Organization.</rdfs:comment>
