    <rdfs:comment>Alias-style refinement kept for depth-3 demonstration under the Human branch; equivalent in scope to SkyPerson but modeled as its dedicated subclass to show a 3rd tier under Human -&gt; SkyPerson -&gt; SkyPersonHuman.</rdfs:comment>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/nikos/ontologies/2026/6/untitled-ontology-29#MultiSkilledCrewmate">
